      "body" : "It worked all transactions are no longer purged at startup, however even with `datacarrier=0`, inscriptions still appear in my mempool(I don't know if it still works for inscriptions of more than 80 bytes).\r\n\r\nWe can see it [here](https://orangepill.ovh/fr/block/00000000000000000002561e1e9e110add7e63f716c3b460499d7b1445f93d1f), as my node refuses the inscriptions they are supposed to appear in blue however we see that many of them have still passed. ",
